The '''''Corellian Horticultural Digest''''' was a gardening journal on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]], published on [[Datacard/Legends|datacards]].<ref name="ijedi">''[[I, Jedi]]''</ref> Its first issue was published nearly three [[Standard century/Legends|centuries]] before the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]].<ref name="swgalaxies">{{GalaxiesAED}} &mdash; Terminal Mission "Horticultural Researcher Under Siege"</ref> The journal's articles covered horticulture, but its editorial staff also sent researchers all over Corellia's landscape to report on the planet's wild plant life. [[Rostek Horn]] wrote several columns for this publication, encrypting messages to [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] in the genetic codes.<ref name="ijedi" />

In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]] one of the journal's researchers was following a lead regarding ''trioecious cycad carpophylls'' when he stumbled into a lair of dangerous beasts. He hid in a safe place and called the journal's staff before his [[Comlink/Legends|comlink]] was eaten. The journal immediately hired a [[Spacer/Legends|spacer]] who killed the creatures and rescued the researcher.<ref name="swgalaxies" />

